# NOTE: mythic-cord/infrarust/ is intentionally NOT ignored — the vendored
# subtree is committed so fresh clones and CI build without re-running the
# vendor script. Re-baselining is `tools/vendor-infrarust.{sh,ps1} <ref>`.

# Texture pack reference bases — third-party packs we use as visual references,
